        "top_heading": "<p>The Story</p>",
        "top_text": "<p>The Roberto Coin brand was born in 1996 when its founder left a successful career in hospitality to pursue his passion for art and fashion. Guided by creativity and imagination, he collaborated with Italy's finest jewelry artisans to craft pieces that transcend jewelry - each one a work of art.</p>",
